{"tid":1892296,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"杜汶澤暗諷李力持遭拒賣","createTime":"2020-02-22T12:08:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T12:31:04.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4060a05f7a201f81a681da394c5610a104a2a1e2","tid":1892296,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T12:08:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200222/3UNVVNBX3QHQ4XYQXM77JTFZXQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200222%2F3UNVVNBX3QHQ4XYQXM77JTFZXQ%2F&d=l2jL6rfoxymyXK22uA%2Bdgt9AtAt3lYzSqFOpIRNeugk%3D&h=5f4783a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200222%2F3UNVVNBX3QHQ4XYQXM77JTFZXQ%2F&h=1bdba2e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200222/3UNVVNBX3QHQ4XYQXM77JTFZXQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n杜汶澤暗諷李力持遭拒賣<br />\n<br />\n不時於社交平台撐內地政府的導演李力持，昨日在攝影器材店的社交網站菲林相機帖文下留言「$？」，疑似店主即留言「唔X賣畀你呀，X樣」，旋即獲近2,500個讚好及心心。網民大讚疑似店主「天地有正義，做得好呀，兄弟」，有網民搞笑指李力持出價多少他多付一元，有網民亦指出「在香港，絕對有權唔做某某生意」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200222/large/1582293643_2b08.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200222%2Flarge%2F1582293643_2b08.jpg&h=7c5476f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n杜汶澤（圖）見李力持買相機被拒，加入留言。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n李力持於留言14小時後，以諧音粗口留言反擊：「睇你班XXXX樣可以做乜！一班廢物！come on X樣」、「不停打XX」，似乎被網民一窩蜂的狠批刺激，雙方掀起罵戰。幾乎同一時間，早前自資買口罩、漂白水送予香港人的杜汶澤亦加入留言：「2部thanks」，秒速獲近2,000網民讚好。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：盧妹<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200222/large/1582293642_a71a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200222%2Flarge%2F1582293642_a71a.jpg&h=42b1a5fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李力持"},{"pid":"9b47940d037d90ed4fcd63cb8a24f7456e61b6e6","tid":1892296,"uid":237555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T12:12:05.000Z","msg":"依條撚樣準備比單野我識笑"},{"pid":"9933fd369ef18320cab48eb4d37326d9f68493c0","tid":1892296,"uid":331949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T12:12:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/izCWpyL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FizCWpyL.png&h=48005c1e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7aac779c3d9f888ccd5078aa710ce8c58ede0d04","tid":1892296,"uid":237555,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b47940d037d90ed4fcd63cb8a24f7456e61b6e6","tid":1892296,"uid":237555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T12:12:05.000Z","msg":"依條撚樣準備比單野我識笑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T12:12:23.000Z","msg":"終於<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de4ddde54935426d303e0c5683ec1f82e7e891dd","tid":1892296,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T12:13:14.000Z","msg":"面就人地畀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c4b7dc7d3458fb29658f3d9bc2e3aa7b15eb19c","tid":1892296,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T12:31:04.000Z","msg":"有冇原文link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}